0C3C1793.Line13.BF6E6: Of course, Daughter of Hatred. With my gift you will face your father. We all return home in the end.

72467205.Line11.BD31C: Fulfill the promise you made to me.

C50EA008.Line9.BF6E6: And you look less well than when I saw you last. I would not be so certain of victory.

F7313382.Line3.BF6E6: So here you are at last, to collect your safe passage to the Cathedral of Hatred.
